## üìñ About The Project

**Phitku** is a fully functional e-commerce platform designed for selling natural personal care products. It provides a seamless shopping experience for customers and a powerful dashboard for administrators to manage inventory.

Built using the **MERN Stack** (MongoDB, Express, React, Node.js), this project demonstrates full-stack development capabilities, including secure authentication, cloud image storage, and responsive design.

---

## ‚ú® Key Features

### üë§ **User Features**
* **Authentication:** Secure Login & Registration (JWT & Bcrypt).
* **Browse & Filter:** Filter products by Category, Price, and Availability.
* **Shopping Cart:** Add/Remove items and adjust quantities.
* **Product Details:** View detailed descriptions, pricing, and ratings.
* **Responsive Design:** Optimized for Mobile, Tablet, and Desktop.

### üõ°Ô∏è **Admin Dashboard**
* **Product Management:** Add, Edit, and Delete products.
* **Image Upload:** Integrated **Cloudinary** for drag-and-drop image uploads.
* **Order Management:** View customer orders and update shipping status (Pending -> Shipped -> Delivered).
* **Secure Access:** Protected routes restrict access to Admin users only.

---

## üõ†Ô∏è Tech Stack

| Component | Technology |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend** | React.js, Tailwind CSS, Lucide Icons, React Router |
| **Backend** | Node.js, Express.js |
| **Database** | MongoDB Atlas (Cloud) |
| **Storage** | Cloudinary (Image Hosting) |
| **Deployment** | GitHub Pages (Frontend), Render (Backend) |

